name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: Read Gov. Chafee's State of the State Address -- "Moving Rhode Island Forward -- at http://t.co/Hd67pTwC

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: Look forward to moving toward a brighter future for our great state #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: The state of our state is steadily improving #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: And we’re doing this without raising taxes or fees and while lowering the corporate tax #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: We are investing in our cities and towns and property tax relief #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: We are investing in workforce development #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: We are investing in infrastructure #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: In this budget, we are investing in education #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: The steps we have taken are working. Rhode Island is working #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: my priorities are reflected in this budget #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: we must support service members and their families, during and after service #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: Let’s come together to pass marriage equality #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: I will work with General Assembly on legislation that makes Rhode Island safer for our children #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: Things are getting better, and we must build on this momentum #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: The results indicate that we are moving steadily in the right direction #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: We want to have a state where there are jobs and opportunities for our children and their children #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: Our ultimate goal is to get our people back to work #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: with a stronger economy and more Rhode Islanders working, all challenges become more manageable #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: I also propose modifying the historic tax credit program by providing access to abandoned tax credits #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: $30 million for local aid & property tax relief #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: $600,000 for tourism marketing efforts #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: $500,000 to accelerate economic activity in 195 land #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: valuable resources put toward repair and improvement, not interest on debt #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: my Administration has also taken historic steps to reform how we finance our transportation system #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: this budget includes a number of strategic infrastructure investments #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: I propose $3 million in new state support for workforce development initiatives #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: I propose an increase of $6 million for no higher education tuition increase #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: $14 million to support repairs at vocational education facilities #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: Budget fully funds the K-12 formula: $30.3 million in additional state education aid this year #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: My commitment to education continues with this budget #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: important to keep investing in education, infrastructure, and workforce development #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: Also propose lowering our corporate tax from 9.0 percent to 7.0 percent over the next three years #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: The budget I present to you tonight contains no increase in taxes, fees, or charges of any kind #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: Budget submitted earliest date in over two decades #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
text: Anyone wondering what my priorities are should read the budget I submit tonight. #RI2013

name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
